  "rationale": "Single sanctioned hero bookend reusing the seeded project pattern hero-display-over-staggered-media verbatim in structure: centered colossal Melodrama display title over two hard-edged photos, the offset portrait crossing the landscape's lower edge (media-over-media overlap + stagger), sanctioned text-on-media title, dark inverse surface carrying the sole gold accent on the display title. Only the DENSITY axis is varied per directive \u2014 the lede collapses to a terse 3-word imperative fragment ('Woodgrain, light, geometry.') and the CTA becomes the action pair 'Buy Tickets \u2014 plan your visit'. Eyebrow and headline are kept verbatim, asset:null defers to brand photography, nothing repositions. novelty:'adapt', seededFrom the project hero pattern."
